descript.abstract: This data represents the transportation sectors used by the City of Baltimore's Department of Transportation, and is used for general mapping/analysis purposes. The contact information provided with this feature class is for each sectors Transportation Liaison. The liaison's are housed in the Department of Transportations Planning Division.
